snippet.title: Reaction to New Amber Heard Audio (PSYCHO)
snippet.description:
#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #AmberHeardAudio

A clip from the GZE podcast about this Johnny Depp Amber Heard situation, we show the new uncensored audio where she says "no one will believe" him, & we give our opinions on the Amber Heard in the Me Too movement, & our reaction to the situation as a whole. Truly chilling situation & we hope our video sheds some light on the type of things men can also deal with in domestic violence & toxic relationships  || Hit the like button if you enjoyed the video!
